# AI Usage Declaration

Large language model (LLM)-based AI tools, including ChatGPT, were used during the development and documentation of this project.

AI assistance was primarily used for:

- Wording refinement
- Quarto/HTML formatting and website structuring
- Minor code formatting suggestions

All experimental design, biological interpretation, calcium imaging workflows, data generation, data analysis logic, and scientific conclusions were developed and verified by the author.

The HLCaTrace workflow, package structure, and associated experimental strategies were built upon the author’s own experimental datasets, analytical needs, and long-term workflow development in collaboration with Dr. Kozo Hamada.
